fields.bio: Dr. Jane Doe is a highly experienced dermatologist with over 10 years of expertise in treating a wide range of skin conditions. After completing her medical degree at Harvard University and a dermatology residency at Mayo Clinic, she has gained extensive experience in both medical and cosmetic dermatology. Dr. Doe is passionate about helping her patients achieve healthier, more radiant skin through personalized care and advanced treatments. As a board-certified dermatologist, she continuously stays up-to-date with the latest advancements in skin care to provide the best outcomes for her patients.

fields.bio:
Dr. Don  Mehta is a highly trained and patient-focused Neurologist with over 10 years of clinical experience in diagnosing and managing a wide spectrum of neurological disorders. After earning his MBBS from Maulana Azad Medical College, he pursued specialization in Internal Medicine at AIIMS, followed by a super-specialty degree in Neurology from the prestigious NIMHANS, Bangalore.

His expertise spans stroke management, epilepsy, migraine, movement disorders, multiple sclerosis, and neuromuscular diseases. Dr. Mehta is known for his methodical diagnostic approach and his ability to explain complex neurological conditions in simple, reassuring terms.

He remains committed to lifelong learning and has recently completed a fellowship in Stroke and Neurocritical Care from the Cleveland Clinic. His dedication to cutting-edge research and compassionate care makes him a sought-after neurologist for both acute and chronic neurological care.

fields.bio:
Dr. Emily Larson is a board-certified Gynecologist and Obstetrician with over 10 years of experience in women's health. A gold medalist during her MBBS at Lady Hardinge Medical College, she pursued her MD in Obstetrics and Gynecology from AIIMS New Delhi, one of the most prestigious medical institutions in India.

She specializes in high-risk pregnancies, infertility treatment, PCOS management, minimally invasive gynecologic surgeries, and adolescent health counseling. Dr. Larson has also completed fellowships in Reproductive Medicine and Laparoscopic Surgery, making her a trusted expert in both medical and surgical management of gynecological conditions.

Her patient-first philosophy, gentle communication, and clinical precision have earned her the trust of hundreds of women across all age groups. Dr. Larson is passionate about educating her patients and empowering them to make informed decisions about their reproductive and general health.

fields.bio:
Dr. Timothy White is a dedicated and highly skilled Gynecologist with over 10 years of experience in women's reproductive health. He completed his MBBS at Grant Medical College, Mumbai, followed by a Master’s in Obstetrics and Gynecology at KEM Hospital, where he received extensive training in both routine and complex gynecological cases.

Dr. White’s areas of expertise include prenatal care, high-risk pregnancy management, infertility treatment, menstrual disorders, and minimally invasive gynecologic surgeries. He has also received advanced training in reproductive endocrinology, allowing him to provide holistic care to women facing fertility challenges.

Renowned for his professional approach and empathetic communication, Dr. White combines clinical excellence with personalized care. He strongly believes in educating his patients and promoting a supportive environment to ensure their comfort and confidence throughout treatment.

fields.bio:
Dr. Ryan Martinez is a compassionate and accomplished Gynecologist with over 10 years of experience in women's health and reproductive care. He earned his MBBS from Madras Medical College, followed by a Master’s in Obstetrics and Gynecology from the prestigious CMC Vellore. His deep clinical training and continued specialization in reproductive technologies and laparoscopic surgery have made him a trusted name in gynecological care.

Dr. Martinez focuses on a wide range of services including fertility treatment, menstrual disorders, high-risk pregnancies, PCOS management, and minimally invasive procedures. With a global perspective from his advanced training in Germany, he brings both innovation and empathy to every patient interaction.

His approach is rooted in respectful, informative care—empowering women with the knowledge and support they need at every stage of life.

fields.bio:
Dr. Zoe Kelly is a dedicated Neurologist with over a decade of experience in treating a wide range of neurological conditions. After completing her MBBS from Government Medical College, Kozhikode, she pursued her MD in General Medicine at PGIMER, Chandigarh, and then earned a super-specialization in Neurology from NIMHANS, one of India’s premier institutions for neurosciences.

Her clinical interests include epilepsy, Parkinson’s disease, stroke, dementia, headache disorders, and neuromuscular conditions. Dr. Kelly is especially skilled in EEG interpretation, neurodiagnostics, and long-term care for chronic neurological conditions.

Known for her compassionate and clear communication, she is deeply committed to educating her patients and ensuring they receive holistic and personalized neurological care. She continues to expand her knowledge through fellowships and international collaborations in neurophysiology.

fields.bio:
Dr. Jennifer Garcia is a board-certified Neurologist with over 10 years of experience in diagnosing and managing a broad range of neurological disorders. After earning her MBBS from St. John’s Medical College, she completed her MD in General Medicine at KMC Manipal, followed by a DM in Neurology from the prestigious NIMHANS, Bangalore.

She has specialized expertise in epilepsy, stroke care, multiple sclerosis, headaches, and movement disorders. Her international training at UCLH, UK, in advanced neurophysiology and stroke management has further refined her approach to evidence-based and globally benchmarked care.

Dr. Garcia is widely respected for her patient-centered approach, in-depth diagnostic skills, and commitment to continuous learning. She believes in empowering patients through education and collaborative treatment planning, ensuring compassionate care for every individual.

fields.bio:
Dr. Andrew Williams is an experienced and trusted Gastroenterologist with over a decade of expertise in treating disorders of the digestive system, liver, pancreas, and intestines. After completing his MBBS from Stanley Medical College, he pursued specialization in Internal Medicine at CMC Vellore, followed by a DM in Gastroenterology at the renowned SGPGIMS, Lucknow.

His areas of interest include acid reflux, IBS, IBD (Crohn’s & ulcerative colitis), liver diseases, endoscopic procedures, and pancreatic disorders. He has also completed an advanced fellowship in therapeutic endoscopy and hepatology, enhancing his capabilities in minimally invasive diagnostics and interventions.

Dr. Williams is known for his meticulous approach, empathetic consultations, and up-to-date treatment methods. His patient-first philosophy ensures that each individual receives comprehensive and personalized gastrointestinal care.

fields.bio:
Dr. Patrick Harris is a highly qualified Gastroenterologist with over 10 years of clinical experience in treating complex digestive and liver conditions. He completed his MBBS from Grant Medical College, followed by an MD in General Medicine from KEM Hospital, Mumbai. His super-specialization in Gastroenterology was earned at AIIMS, New Delhi, one of India’s top institutes.

He specializes in liver diseases, inflammatory bowel disease (IBD), GERD, gastrointestinal bleeding, pancreatitis, and endoscopic procedures. With a focus on evidence-based medicine and minimally invasive care, Dr. Harris ensures accurate diagnosis and efficient management of both acute and chronic digestive disorders.

Known for his compassionate care, clear communication, and updated clinical knowledge, Dr. Harris is committed to delivering personalized gastrointestinal healthcare with precision and empathy.

fields.bio:
Dr. Ava Mitchell is a board-certified Dermatologist with over 8 years of specialized experience in medical, surgical, and cosmetic skin care. After completing her MBBS at Grant Medical College, Mumbai, she pursued an MD in Dermatology at KEM Hospital, where she trained extensively in managing conditions such as acne, eczema, psoriasis, and complex skin infections.

Her additional fellowships in cosmetic dermatology, laser therapies, and dermoscopy equip her to offer advanced aesthetic treatments—ranging from anti-aging injectables and chemical peels to laser resurfacing and mole mapping. Known for her meticulous clinical assessments and gentle chair-side manner, Dr. Mitchell emphasizes a personalized, evidence-based approach to both restore skin health and enhance natural beauty.

She regularly contributes to dermatology journals and participates in international conferences to stay at the forefront of emerging therapies and technologies in skincare.

fields.bio:
Dr. Amelia Hill is a skilled and compassionate Dermatologist with over 9 years of experience in diagnosing and treating a wide spectrum of skin, hair, and nail disorders. A graduate of Osmania Medical College, she furthered her specialization with an MD from JIPMER, one of India’s top medical institutes.

She has expertise in both clinical and cosmetic dermatology, including acne treatment, pigmentation disorders, psoriasis, vitiligo, hair loss, and laser therapies. Her international training has sharpened her skills in anti-aging treatments, chemical peels, microneedling, and scar revision.

Dr. Hill is known for her holistic and ethical approach to skin health, combining clinical precision with aesthetic finesse. She takes pride in customizing treatment plans that suit individual skin types and concerns, ensuring natural and lasting results.

fields.bio:
Dr. Christopher Lee is a dedicated and experienced Pediatrician with over 10 years of clinical practice in child health. He obtained his MBBS from BMCRI, Bengaluru, and completed his postgraduate specialization in Pediatrics from PGIMER, one of India’s leading institutions. He also holds specialized training in pediatric emergency care and child nutrition.

Dr. Lee is passionate about providing compassionate, comprehensive, and child-friendly care for infants, toddlers, and teenagers. His areas of interest include newborn care, vaccination, developmental monitoring, childhood infections, and allergies. With his gentle demeanor and strong communication with both children and parents, he fosters a trusting and comfortable environment in his clinic.

He believes in preventive pediatrics and works closely with parents to promote healthy habits and early developmental support for children.

fields.bio:
Dr. Jeffrey King is a board-certified Pediatrician with over 9 years of experience in child healthcare and wellness. A graduate of Maulana Azad Medical College, he pursued his MD in Pediatrics at Lady Hardinge Medical College, one of India’s premier pediatric institutions. He has further trained in pediatric pulmonology and infectious diseases.

Dr. King provides expert care in immunizations, asthma and allergy management, developmental screening, common childhood illnesses, and nutritional counseling. He is known for his warm, approachable manner and his ability to build rapport with both children and their parents.

He strongly believes in preventive care and early intervention, aiming to ensure every child reaches their fullest health and developmental potential.
